## Overview

Rule 4 defines the **complete authorization pipeline** from strategy signals through risk governance to authorized trades. The [CentralRiskManager](mdc:core_engine/system/central_risk_manager.py) serves as the **SINGLE POINT OF AUTHORITY** for ALL trading decisions.

**Key Principle:** ALL trading decisions MUST flow through CentralRiskManager authorization. NO component can execute trades independently.

