## Position Management Authority (CRITICAL)

### SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH: CentralRiskManager

**The CentralRiskManager is the ONLY component that can update positions.**

### Position Update Flow (MANDATORY)

```python
# MANDATORY: All position updates flow through RiskManager
class CentralRiskManager:
    async def update_position(
        self, 
        symbol: str, 
        side: str, 
        quantity: float, 
        price: float, 
        timestamp: datetime
    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """
        Update position and notify all components
        
        ONLY THIS METHOD can modify positions.
        """
        # Get current position
        current_position = self.current_positions.get(symbol, 0.0)
        
        # Calculate new position
        if side.lower() == 'buy':
            new_position = current_position + quantity
            self.available_cash -= (quantity * price)  # Reduce cash
        elif side.lower() == 'sell':
            new_position = current_position - quantity
            self.available_cash += (quantity * price)  # Increase cash
        
        # Update position
        self.current_positions[symbol] = new_position
        
        # Record position change in history
        position_change = {
            'timestamp': timestamp,
            'symbol': symbol,
            'side': side,
            'quantity': quantity,
            'price': price,
            'previous_position': current_position,
            'new_position': new_position,
            'position_value': new_position * price
        }
        self.position_history.append(position_change)
        
        # Update portfolio metrics
        self._update_portfolio_metrics()
        
        # NOTIFY all dependent components
        await self._notify_position_change(position_change)
        
        return {
            'symbol': symbol,
            'position': new_position,
            'position_value': new_position * price,
            'portfolio_value': self.portfolio_value,
            'available_cash': self.available_cash
        }
    
    async def _notify_position_change(self, position_change: Dict[str, Any]):
        """Notify all components of position update"""
        # Notify Portfolio Manager (read-only)
        if self.portfolio_manager:
            await self.portfolio_manager.on_position_update(position_change)
        
        # Notify Analytics Engine (read-only)
        if self.analytics_engine:
            await self.analytics_engine.on_position_update(position_change)
        
        # Notify Risk Monitoring (read-only)
        if self.risk_monitor:
            await self.risk_monitor.on_position_update(position_change)
```

